'''圣约翰伍德教堂'''（St John's Wood Church）是一个[[圣公会|圣公会]]牧区，位于伦敦[[圣约翰伍德|圣约翰伍德]]的罗德环岛（Lord's Roundabout），介于[[罗德板球场|罗德板球场]]（Lord's Cricket Ground）与[[摄政公园|摄政公园]]之间，被英国遗产委员会列为二级登录建筑<ref>English Heritage, [http://list.english-heritage.org.uk/resultsingle.aspx?uid=1264852 "List entry 1264852"] {{Wayback|url=http://list.english-heritage.org.uk/resultsingle.aspx?uid=1264852 |date=20140502024124 }}.2014-01-08</ref>。牧区隶属于查令十字会吏长区。

该堂兴建于1814年，建筑师托马斯·哈德威克，他同时建造了目前的圣马里波恩教堂<ref>St Marylebone Parish Church website, [http://www.stmarylebone.org/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=124&Itemid=265 "Architectural Details"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.stmarylebone.org/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=124&Itemid=265 |date=20141006091511 }}. 2013-11-18.</ref> 。教堂原有大片1814墓地，于1855年关闭，1886年改为公共花园圣约翰伍德教堂庭园（St. John's Wood Church Grounds）<ref>London Gardens Online, [http://www.londongardensonline.org.uk/gardens-online-record.asp?ID=WST109 "St John's Wood Church Grounds"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.londongardensonline.org.uk/gardens-online-record.asp?ID=WST109 |date=20131019120601 }}. Retrieved 18 November 2013.</ref>。[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]之后，因圣士提反堂被炸弹破坏，圣约翰伍德教堂在1952年成为牧区教堂<ref>St John's Wood Memories, [http://www.stjohnswoodmemories.org.uk/page_id__89_path__0p55p.aspx "St John's Church"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.stjohnswoodmemories.org.uk/page_id__89_path__0p55p.aspx |date=20141006103655 }}.2013-11-18.</ref>。1969年，[[保罗·麦卡特尼|保罗·麦卡特尼]]和琳达的婚礼在此举行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://marriage.about.com/od/entertainmen1/a/mccartneylinda.htm |title=Paul McCartney and Linda Eastman Marriage Profile |publisher=Marriage.about.com |date= |accessdate=2013-11-12 |archive-date=2013-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021115911/http://marriage.about.com/od/entertainmen1/a/mccartneylinda.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 

[[File:St_John's_Wood_Church.jpg|thumb]]
今日，该堂有225名在册信徒，其中有130〜150名信徒定期参加礼拜<ref>Diocese of London website, [http://www.london.anglican.org/about/explore-the-diocese/parish/st-john-s-wood-church// "St John's Wood Church"].2013-11-18</ref>。建筑物向外开放，作为祈祷和默想的地点<ref>St John's Wood High Street, [http://stjohnswoodhighstreet.com/local-services/pages/st-johns-wood-church/ "St John's Wood Church"] {{Wayback|url=http://stjohnswoodhighstreet.com/local-services/pages/st-johns-wood-church/ |date=20140930160732 }}.2013-11-18</ref>。

圣约翰伍德教堂与其他教堂合作，每月为[[大赦国际|大赦国际]]共同举办仪式<ref>St John's Wood Church website, [http://www.stjohnswoodchurch.org.uk/pattern-of-services/study-prayer "Study & Prayer"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.stjohnswoodchurch.org.uk/pattern-of-services/study-prayer |date=20131112142005 }}.2013-11-18</ref>。该堂牧师还与犹太会堂和[[伦敦中央清真寺|伦敦中央清真寺]]的代表会面，进行经文研究（scriptural reasoning）讨论。

